main event: An unidentified object resembling a star-like object was observed in a cloudy sky on July 5, 1967.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 45 minutes, The object disappeared and reappeared multiple times, The witness described the object as having a whirring sound, The observed object was reported as cigar-shaped, The object was noted to have reddish or pinkish lights.
witness description: male, age 39, reported seeing the object in the front yard.
